======================================================================
REPRODUCTION: TorchTitan attn_backend mismatch bug
======================================================================
torchtitan version: 0.2.2
torchtitan location: /workspace/torchtitan-src/torchtitan/__init__.py

[1] model_registry signature for llama3:
    model_registry(flavor: str, attn_backend: str = 'sdpa') -> torchtitan.protocols.model_spec.ModelSpec
    → attn_backend default = 'sdpa'

[2] Calling model_registry('debugmodel') — same as verl upstream code:
    verl code: model_spec = model_module.model_registry(torchtitan_flavor)
    → does NOT pass attn_backend, so it defaults to 'sdpa'
    model_spec.model type: Config
    model_spec.model has 'layer':  False
    model_spec.model has 'layers': True

[3] verl upstream's override path (transformer_impl.py L113-115):
    engine_config.attn_type = 'flex'
    verl code: if hasattr(model_spec.model, 'layer') and ...
    hasattr(model_spec.model, 'layer') = False
    → GUARD FAILED — model_spec.model has 'layers' (plural), NOT 'layer'
    → The override NEVER RUNS. attn_backend stays as sdpa.

[4] Actual attention config in model_spec (after verl's failed 'override'):
    inner_attention type: Config
    mask_type: causal
    ✗ ACTUAL backend = 'sdpa' (should be 'flex')
    ✗ BUG CONFIRMED: model built with 'sdpa' despite user requesting 'flex'

[5] CORRECT FIX — pass attn_backend to model_registry():
    model_spec = model_module.model_registry(flavor, attn_backend=attn_type)
    inner_attention type: Config
    mask_type: block_causal
    ✓ ACTUAL backend = 'flex' — CORRECT!

[6] Verify fix also works for attn_type='varlen':
    ✓ varlen backend correctly set

======================================================================
SUMMARY:
  Bug location: verl/workers/engine/torchtitan/transformer_impl.py
  Root cause #1: model_registry() called without attn_backend param
                 → always defaults to 'sdpa'
  Root cause #2: Fallback uses 'layer' (singular) but config has 'layers'
                 → guard always fails, override never runs
  Impact: ALL users get sdpa even when they set attn_type=flex/varlen
  Fix: Pass attn_backend=attn_type to model_registry()
  Scope: Affects ALL hardware (CUDA, NPU, XPU)
======================================================================
